Nine companies bid for US Stockpile germanium . Nine companies , including producers , bid for germanium metal offered for the first time by the U . S . Stockpile . The Stockpile was offering 4 , 000 kilos in the current fiscal year . Lattice bid for 139 kilograms at prices ranging from $ 900 to $ 1 , 400 per kilo . DRT International bid for 501 kilos at $ 100 per kilo . Atomergic Chemetals bid for 1 , 000 kilos at $ 600 per kilo . Eagle Picher Industries bid for 4 , 000 kilos at $ 1 , 251 per kilo . Mistral Inc bid for 517 kilos at $ 1 , 100 to $ 1 , 300 a kilo . American Xtel Tech bid for 4 , 000 kilos at $ 1 , 525 to $ 500 per kilo . Laser Diode Inc bid for 2 , 000 kilos at $ 1 , 405 to $ 1 , 150 a kilo . Metaleurop bid for 2 , 000 kilos at $ 980 to $ 800 a kilo . GFI Advanced Tech bid for 100 kilos at $ 1 , 207 to $ 1 , 137 a kilo . ( ( New York Commodity Desk 212 - 859 - 1646 ) ) 
